    "To resolve such cases, we used a convention of separating the entities with the symbols \" &&\" for parsing individual relationships from sentence with multiple entities.",
    "This convention was shown to the LLM with some examples in the prompt (see Fig. 2 second example).",
    "This enabled us to better parse the output after generation.",
    "Entity AggregationOur approach with this work consisted in extracting all the insights from literature as opposed to querying the sentence dataset with a pre-defined list of phase and properties.",
    "An entity aggregation step is therefore needed in our framework to consolidate the different extracted entities into a smaller list of phases and properties."
